---

<section class="masterplan" id="masterplan">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Site Plan</span>
      <h2>Master Plan Kawasan</h2>
      <p>
        Zoning yang jelas — tidak ada satu rumah pun yang berbatasan langsung
        dengan jalan utama.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="masterplan__visual">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524661135-423995f22d0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80"
        alt="Master plan kawasan Haventerra Residence Tangerang Selatan"
      />
      <div class="masterplan__overlay"></div>
      <div class="masterplan__legend">
        <span class="legend-item">🏠 Hunian</span>
        <span class="legend-item">🌳 Ruang Hijau 30%</span>
        <span class="legend-item">🏊 Clubhouse & Pool</span>
        <span class="legend-item">🎮 Children Park</span>
        <span class="legend-item">🛒 Area Komersial</span>
        <span class="legend-item">🛡️ Security Post</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .masterplan {
    background: var(--color-warm-cream);
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
  }
  .masterplan__visual {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--rounded-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 7;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .masterplan__visual img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .masterplan__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(8, 18, 12, 0.5) 0%,
      transparent 60%
    );
  }
  .masterplan__legend {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 13px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    border-radius: var(--rounded-full);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .masterplan__visual {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }
  }
</style>
